{
  "video_id": "ydKcaIE6O1k",
  "title": "Poverty isn't a lack of character; it's a lack of cash | Rutger Bregman",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13395.0,
      "end_time": 16502.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to start with a simple question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17820.0,
      "end_time": 21660.0,
      "text": "Why do the poor make so many poor decisions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23672.0,
      "end_time": 25223.0,
      "text": "I know it&#39;s a harsh question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25247.0,
      "end_time": 27212.0,
      "text": "but take a look at the data."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27236.0,
      "end_time": 29790.0,
      "text": "The poor borrow more, save less,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29103.0,
      "end_time": 31762.0,
      "text": "smoke more, exercise less, drink more"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31786.0,
      "end_time": 33306.0,
      "text": "and eat less healthfully."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34192.0,
      "end_time": 35353.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36271.0,
      "end_time": 37798.0,
      "text": "Well, the standard explanation"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37822.0,
      "end_time": 41202.0,
      "text": "was once summed up by the British Prime Minister, Margaret Thatcher."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41226.0,
      "end_time": 44611.0,
      "text": "And she called poverty \"a personality defect.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44635.0,
      "end_time": 46475.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46499.0,
      "end_time": 48405.0,
      "text": "A lack of character, basically."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49285.0,
      "end_time": 53275.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m sure not many of you would be so blunt."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54317.0,
      "end_time": 58167.0,
      "text": "But the idea that there&#39;s something wrong with the poor themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58191.0,
      "end_time": 60174.0,
      "text": "is not restricted to Mrs. Thatcher."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61105.0,
      "end_time": 64307.0,
      "text": "Some of you may believe that the poor should be held responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64331.0,
      "end_time": 66850.0,
      "text": "for their own mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66109.0,
      "end_time": 70600.0,
      "text": "And others may argue that we should help them to make better decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70674.0,
      "end_time": 73903.0,
      "text": "But the underlying assumption is the same:"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74470.0,
      "end_time": 77440.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s something wrong with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77877.0,
      "end_time": 79735.0,
      "text": "If we could just change them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79759.0,
      "end_time": 82251.0,
      "text": "if we could just teach them how to live their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82275.0,
      "end_time": 83808.0,
      "text": "if they would only listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85530.0,
      "end_time": 86750.0,
      "text": "And to be honest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86774.0,
      "end_time": 90112.0,
      "text": "this was what I thought for a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90898.0,
      "end_time": 93120.0,
      "text": "It was only a few years ago that I discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93360.0,
      "end_time": 96533.0,
      "text": "that everything I thought I knew about poverty was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98106.0,
      "end_time": 100756.0,
      "text": "It all started when I accidentally stumbled upon a paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100781.0,
      "end_time": 102389.0,
      "text": "by a few American psychologists."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102413.0,
      "end_time": 104966.0,
      "text": "They had traveled 8,000 miles, all the way to India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104990.0,
      "end_time": 106565.0,
      "text": "for a fascinating study."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107650.0,
      "end_time": 109833.0,
      "text": "And it was an experiment with sugarcane farmers."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110658.0,
      "end_time": 114600.0,
      "text": "You should know that these farmers collect about 60 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114300.0,
      "end_time": 116163.0,
      "text": "of their annual income all at once,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116187.0,
      "end_time": 117895.0,
      "text": "right after the harvest."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117919.0,
      "end_time": 121459.0,
      "text": "This means that they&#39;re relatively poor one part of the year"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121483.0,
      "end_time": 123770.0,
      "text": "and rich the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124415.0,
      "end_time": 128471.0,
      "text": "The researchers asked them to do an IQ test before and after the harvest."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129722.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133742.0,
      "text": "What they subsequently discovered completely blew my mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134979.0,
      "end_time": 139428.0,
      "text": "The farmers scored much worse on the test before the harvest."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 140277.0,
      "end_time": 142577.0,
      "text": "The effects of living in poverty, it turns out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142601.0,
      "end_time": 145969.0,
      "text": "correspond to losing 14 points of IQ."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145993.0,
      "end_time": 147862.0,
      "text": "Now, to give you an idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147886.0,
      "end_time": 150327.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s comparable to losing a night&#39;s sleep"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 150351.0,
      "end_time": 152524.0,
      "text": "or the effects of alcoholism."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154505.0,
      "end_time": 156763.0,
      "text": "A few months later, I heard that Eldar Shafir,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156788.0,
      "end_time": 160335.0,
      "text": "a professor at Princeton University and one of the authors of this study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 160359.0,
      "end_time": 162678.0,
      "text": "was coming over to Holland, where I live."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162702.0,
      "end_time": 164103.0,
      "text": "So we met up in Amsterdam"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164128.0,
      "end_time": 167678.0,
      "text": "to talk about his revolutionary new theory of poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168210.0,
      "end_time": 170313.0,
      "text": "And I can sum it up in just two words:"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 171235.0,
      "end_time": 173252.0,
      "text": "scarcity mentality."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174467.0,
      "end_time": 176621.0,
      "text": "It turns out that people behave differently"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176645.0,
      "end_time": 179131.0,
      "text": "when they perceive a thing to be scarce."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 179155.0,
      "end_time": 181370.0,
      "text": "And what that thing is doesn&#39;t much matter --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 181394.0,
      "end_time": 184407.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s not enough time, money or food."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 184900.0,
      "end_time": 186558.0,
      "text": "You all know this feeling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 186582.0,
      "end_time": 188545.0,
      "text": "when you&#39;ve got too much to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 188569.0,
      "end_time": 190584.0,
      "text": "or when you&#39;ve put off breaking for lunch"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 190609.0,
      "end_time": 192272.0,
      "text": "and your blood sugar takes a dive."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 192296.0,
      "end_time": 195124.0,
      "text": "This narrows your focus to your immediate lack --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 195148.0,
      "end_time": 197158.0,
      "text": "to the sandwich you&#39;ve got to have now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 197182.0,
      "end_time": 199444.0,
      "text": "the meeting that&#39;s starting in five minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 199468.0,
      "end_time": 202346.0,
      "text": "or the bills that have to be paid tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 202868.0,
      "end_time": 206840.0,
      "text": "So the long-term perspective goes out the window."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 207655.0,
      "end_time": 210186.0,
      "text": "You could compare it to a new computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 210210.0,
      "end_time": 212397.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s running 10 heavy programs at once."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 213210.0,
      "end_time": 215793.0,
      "text": "It gets slower and slower, making errors."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 215818.0,
      "end_time": 217640.0,
      "text": "Eventually, it freezes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 217664.0,
      "end_time": 219769.0,
      "text": "not because it&#39;s a bad computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219794.0,
      "end_time": 222414.0,
      "text": "but because it has too much to do at once."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 223279.0,
      "end_time": 226147.0,
      "text": "The poor have the same problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 226654.0,
      "end_time": 229444.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re not making dumb decisions because they are dumb,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 229468.0,
      "end_time": 231390.0,
      "text": "but because they&#39;re living in a context"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 231414.0,
      "end_time": 233757.0,
      "text": "in which anyone would make dumb decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 234362.0,
      "end_time": 237310.0,
      "text": "So suddenly I understood"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 237334.0,
      "end_time": 241300.0,
      "text": "why so many of our anti-poverty programs don&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 242467.0,
      "end_time": 246991.0,
      "text": "Investments in education, for example, are often completely ineffective."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 247150.0,
      "end_time": 249827.0,
      "text": "Poverty is not a lack of knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 250580.0,
      "end_time": 253135.0,
      "text": "A recent analysis of 201 studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 253159.0,
      "end_time": 255471.0,
      "text": "on the effectiveness of money-management training"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 255495.0,
      "end_time": 259244.0,
      "text": "came to the conclusion that it has almost no effect at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 259267.0,
      "end_time": 260712.0,
      "text": "Now, don&#39;t get me wrong --"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 260737.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263233.0,
      "text": "this is not to say the poor don&#39;t learn anything --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 263257.0,
      "end_time": 265162.0,
      "text": "they can come out wiser for sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 265832.0,
      "end_time": 267469.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 267494.0,
      "end_time": 270496.0,
      "text": "Or as Professor Shafir told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 270520.0,
      "end_time": 272503.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s like teaching someone to swim"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 272528.0,
      "end_time": 275554.0,
      "text": "and then throwing them in a stormy sea.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 276508.0,
      "end_time": 278103.0,
      "text": "I still remember sitting there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 279230.0,
      "end_time": 280278.0,
      "text": "perplexed."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 281111.0,
      "end_time": 282268.0,
      "text": "And it struck me"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 282292.0,
      "end_time": 284804.0,
      "text": "that we could have figured this all out decades ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 284829.0,
      "end_time": 288800.0,
      "text": "I mean, these psychologists didn&#39;t need any complicated brain scans;"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 288104.0,
      "end_time": 290113.0,
      "text": "they only had to measure the farmer&#39;s IQ,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 290137.0,
      "end_time": 292645.0,
      "text": "and IQ tests were invented more than 100 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 293390.0,
      "end_time": 296748.0,
      "text": "Actually, I realized I had read about the psychology of poverty before."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 297367.0,
      "end_time": 301410.0,
      "text": "George Orwell, one of the greatest writers who ever lived,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 301650.0,
      "end_time": 303968.0,
      "text": "experienced poverty firsthand in the 1920s."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 304676.0,
      "end_time": 306854.0,
      "text": "\"The essence of poverty,\" he wrote back then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 306878.0,
      "end_time": 309812.0,
      "text": "is that it \"annihilates the future.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 310967.0,
      "end_time": 313154.0,
      "text": "And he marveled at, quote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 313746.0,
      "end_time": 317320.0,
      "text": "\"How people take it for granted they have the right to preach at you"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 317560.0,
      "end_time": 318207.0,
      "text": "and pray over you"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 318231.0,
      "end_time": 320703.0,
      "text": "as soon as your income falls below a certain level.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 320727.0,
      "end_time": 324631.0,
      "text": "Now, those words are every bit as resonant today."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 326965.0,
      "end_time": 328945.0,
      "text": "The big question is, of course:"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 328970.0,
      "end_time": 330310.0,
      "text": "What can be done?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 330334.0,
      "end_time": 333129.0,
      "text": "Modern economists have a few solutions up their sleeves."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 333153.0,
      "end_time": 335212.0,
      "text": "We could help the poor with their paperwork"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 335236.0,
      "end_time": 338218.0,
      "text": "or send them a text message to remind them to pay their bills."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 338242.0,
      "end_time": 342949.0,
      "text": "This type of solution is hugely popular with modern politicians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 342973.0,
      "end_time": 344676.0,
      "text": "mostly because,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 344700.0,
      "end_time": 346760.0,
      "text": "well, they cost next to nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 347955.0,
      "end_time": 351965.0,
      "text": "These solutions are, I think, a symbol of this era"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 351989.0,
      "end_time": 354166.0,
      "text": "in which we so often treat the symptoms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 354190.0,
      "end_time": 356330.0,
      "text": "but ignore the underlying cause."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 357494.0,
      "end_time": 358748.0,
      "text": "So I wonder:"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 359606.0,
      "end_time": 362953.0,
      "text": "Why don&#39;t we just change the context in which the poor live?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 363545.0,
      "end_time": 365670.0,
      "text": "Or, going back to our computer analogy:"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 365694.0,
      "end_time": 367831.0,
      "text": "Why keep tinkering around with the software"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 367855.0,
      "end_time": 371920.0,
      "text": "when we can easily solve the problem by installing some extra memory instead?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 371944.0,
      "end_time": 375342.0,
      "text": "At that point, Professor Shafir responded with a blank look."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 376112.0,
      "end_time": 377749.0,
      "text": "And after a few seconds, he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 378742.0,
      "end_time": 380867.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, I get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 381480.0,
      "end_time": 385211.0,
      "text": "You mean you want to just hand out more money to the poor"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 385964.0,
      "end_time": 387815.0,
      "text": "to eradicate poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 387839.0,
      "end_time": 390640.0,
      "text": "Uh, sure, that&#39;d be great."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 391734.0,
      "end_time": 394340.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m afraid that brand of left-wing politics"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 394590.0,
      "end_time": 395903.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got in Amsterdam --"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 395927.0,
      "end_time": 397590.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t exist in the States.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 398342.0,
      "end_time": 402317.0,
      "text": "But is this really an old-fashioned, leftist idea?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 403214.0,
      "end_time": 405201.0,
      "text": "I remembered reading about an old plan --"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 405225.0,
      "end_time": 408709.0,
      "text": "something that has been proposed by some of history&#39;s leading thinkers."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 408733.0,
      "end_time": 412549.0,
      "text": "The philosopher Thomas More first hinted at it in his book, \"Utopia,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 412573.0,
      "end_time": 414472.0,
      "text": "more than 500 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 415250.0,
      "end_time": 418575.0,
      "text": "And its proponents have spanned the spectrum from the left to the right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 418599.0,
      "end_time": 421369.0,
      "text": "from the civil rights campaigner, Martin Luther King,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 421393.0,
      "end_time": 424143.0,
      "text": "to the economist Milton Friedman."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 425930.0,
      "end_time": 427913.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s an incredibly simple idea:"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 429630.0,
      "end_time": 431698.0,
      "text": "basic income guarantee."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 433285.0,
      "end_time": 434443.0,
      "text": "What it is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 434824.0,
      "end_time": 435986.0,
      "text": "Well, that&#39;s easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 436547.0,
      "end_time": 439278.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a monthly grant, enough to pay for your basic needs:"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 439302.0,
      "end_time": 440980.0,
      "text": "food, shelter, education."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 441503.0,
      "end_time": 443324.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s completely unconditional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 443348.0,
      "end_time": 446108.0,
      "text": "so no one&#39;s going to tell you what you have to do for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 446132.0,
      "end_time": 448950.0,
      "text": "and no one&#39;s going to tell you what you have to do with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 448974.0,
      "end_time": 451264.0,
      "text": "The basic income is not a favor, but a right."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 451288.0,
      "end_time": 453421.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s absolutely no stigma attached."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 454192.0,
      "end_time": 456822.0,
      "text": "So as I learned about the true nature of poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 456846.0,
      "end_time": 458336.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t stop wondering:"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 459280.0,
      "end_time": 461868.0,
      "text": "Is this the idea we&#39;ve all been waiting for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 462518.0,
      "end_time": 464698.0,
      "text": "Could it really be that simple?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 466168.0,
      "end_time": 467968.0,
      "text": "And in the three years that followed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 467992.0,
      "end_time": 470530.0,
      "text": "I read everything I could find about basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 470554.0,
      "end_time": 472491.0,
      "text": "I researched the dozens of experiments"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 472515.0,
      "end_time": 474635.0,
      "text": "that have been conducted all over the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 474660.0,
      "end_time": 477728.0,
      "text": "and it didn&#39;t take long before I stumbled upon a story of a town"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 477752.0,
      "end_time": 480224.0,
      "text": "that had done it -- had actually eradicated poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 480248.0,
      "end_time": 481518.0,
      "text": "But then ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 482298.0,
      "end_time": 483868.0,
      "text": "nearly everyone forgot about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 485406.0,
      "end_time": 487935.0,
      "text": "This story starts in Dauphin, Canada."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 488871.0,
      "end_time": 494450.0,
      "text": "In 1974, everybody in this small town was guaranteed a basic income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 494475.0,
      "end_time": 497210.0,
      "text": "ensuring that no one fell below the poverty line."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 497234.0,
      "end_time": 498830.0,
      "text": "At the start of the experiment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 498854.0,
      "end_time": 502327.0,
      "text": "an army of researchers descended on the town."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 503187.0,
      "end_time": 505718.0,
      "text": "For four years, all went well."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 506331.0,
      "end_time": 509763.0,
      "text": "But then a new government was voted into power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 509787.0,
      "end_time": 513297.0,
      "text": "and the new Canadian cabinet saw little point to the expensive experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 513321.0,
      "end_time": 517574.0,
      "text": "So when it became clear there was no money left to analyze the results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 517597.0,
      "end_time": 522400.0,
      "text": "the researchers decided to pack their files away in some 2,000 boxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 523995.0,
      "end_time": 526785.0,
      "text": "Twenty-five years went by,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 526809.0,
      "end_time": 529497.0,
      "text": "and then Evelyn Forget, a Canadian professor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 529521.0,
      "end_time": 530737.0,
      "text": "found the records."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 530761.0,
      "end_time": 534728.0,
      "text": "For three years, she subjected the data to all manner of statistical analysis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 534752.0,
      "end_time": 536338.0,
      "text": "and no matter what she tried,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 536362.0,
      "end_time": 539980.0,
      "text": "the results were the same every time:"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 539788.0,
      "end_time": 543606.0,
      "text": "the experiment had been a resounding success."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 545131.0,
      "end_time": 546290.0,
      "text": "Evelyn Forget discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 546315.0,
      "end_time": 548899.0,
      "text": "that the people in Dauphin had not only become richer"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 548923.0,
      "end_time": 550454.0,
      "text": "but also smarter and healthier."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 550478.0,
      "end_time": 553983.0,
      "text": "The school performance of kids improved substantially."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 554976.0,
      "end_time": 559204.0,
      "text": "The hospitalization rate decreased by as much as 8.5 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 559942.0,
      "end_time": 561752.0,
      "text": "Domestic violence incidents were down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 561776.0,
      "end_time": 563567.0,
      "text": "as were mental health complaints."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 563973.0,
      "end_time": 566290.0,
      "text": "And people didn&#39;t quit their jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 566329.0,
      "end_time": 570630.0,
      "text": "The only ones who worked a little less were new mothers and students --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 570870.0,
      "end_time": 571532.0,
      "text": "who stayed in school longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 572708.0,
      "end_time": 574583.0,
      "text": "Similar results have since been found"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 574607.0,
      "end_time": 577200.0,
      "text": "in countless other experiments around the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 577270.0,
      "end_time": 579274.0,
      "text": "from the US to India."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 581433.0,
      "end_time": 582653.0,
      "text": "So ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 583500.0,
      "end_time": 584834.0,
      "text": "here&#39;s what I&#39;ve learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 585815.0,
      "end_time": 587971.0,
      "text": "When it comes to poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 587995.0,
      "end_time": 593111.0,
      "text": "we, the rich, should stop pretending we know best."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 594310.0,
      "end_time": 596785.0,
      "text": "We should stop sending shoes and teddy bears to the poor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 596809.0,
      "end_time": 598329.0,
      "text": "to people we have never met."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 598354.0,
      "end_time": 601887.0,
      "text": "And we should get rid of the vast industry of paternalistic bureaucrats"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 601911.0,
      "end_time": 604920.0,
      "text": "when we could simply hand over their salaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 604116.0,
      "end_time": 605922.0,
      "text": "to the poor they&#39;re supposed to help."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 605946.0,
      "end_time": 608242.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 608266.0,
      "end_time": 611139.0,
      "text": "Because, I mean, the great thing about money"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 611163.0,
      "end_time": 613514.0,
      "text": "is that people can use it to buy things they need"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 613538.0,
      "end_time": 616691.0,
      "text": "instead of things that self-appointed experts think they need."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 617702.0,
      "end_time": 622106.0,
      "text": "Just imagine how many brilliant scientists and entrepreneurs and writers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 622130.0,
      "end_time": 623281.0,
      "text": "like George Orwell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 623305.0,
      "end_time": 626940.0,
      "text": "are now withering away in scarcity."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 626119.0,
      "end_time": 628575.0,
      "text": "Imagine how much energy and talent we would unleash"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 628599.0,
      "end_time": 631338.0,
      "text": "if we got rid of poverty once and for all."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 631362.0,
      "end_time": 635714.0,
      "text": "I believe that a basic income would work like venture capital for the people."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 636913.0,
      "end_time": 638957.0,
      "text": "And we can&#39;t afford not to do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 638981.0,
      "end_time": 641826.0,
      "text": "because poverty is hugely expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 642366.0,
      "end_time": 645758.0,
      "text": "Just look at the cost of child poverty in the US, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 645782.0,
      "end_time": 650140.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s estimated at 500 billion dollars each year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 650380.0,
      "end_time": 652986.0,
      "text": "in terms of higher health care spending, higher dropout rates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 653100.0,
      "end_time": 654393.0,
      "text": "and more crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 654417.0,
      "end_time": 658297.0,
      "text": "Now, this is an incredible waste of human potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 660185.0,
      "end_time": 662386.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s talk about the elephant in the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 663146.0,
      "end_time": 666157.0,
      "text": "How could we ever afford a basic income guarantee?"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 666872.0,
      "end_time": 669971.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s actually a lot cheaper than you may think."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 669995.0,
      "end_time": 673559.0,
      "text": "What they did in Dauphin is finance it with a negative income tax."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 673583.0,
      "end_time": 675591.0,
      "text": "This means that your income is topped up"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 675615.0,
      "end_time": 678270.0,
      "text": "as soon as you fall below the poverty line."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 678510.0,
      "end_time": 679413.0,
      "text": "And in that scenario,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 679437.0,
      "end_time": 681951.0,
      "text": "according to our economists&#39; best estimates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 681975.0,
      "end_time": 685000.0,
      "text": "for a net cost of 175 billion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 685240.0,
      "end_time": 689931.0,
      "text": "a quarter of US military spending, one percent of GDP --"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 689955.0,
      "end_time": 693509.0,
      "text": "you could lift all impoverished Americans above the poverty line."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 694386.0,
      "end_time": 697526.0,
      "text": "You could actually eradicate poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 697962.0,
      "end_time": 699764.0,
      "text": "Now, that should be our goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 700536.0,
      "end_time": 701619.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 701644.0,
      "end_time": 704576.0,
      "text": "The time for small thoughts and little nudges is past."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 704600.0,
      "end_time": 707908.0,
      "text": "I really believe that the time has come for radical new ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 707932.0,
      "end_time": 711132.0,
      "text": "and basic income is so much more than just another policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 711156.0,
      "end_time": 715794.0,
      "text": "It is also a complete rethink of what work actually is."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 715818.0,
      "end_time": 717488.0,
      "text": "And in that sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 717512.0,
      "end_time": 719304.0,
      "text": "it will not only free the poor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 720352.0,
      "end_time": 721819.0,
      "text": "but also the rest of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 723810.0,
      "end_time": 725327.0,
      "text": "Nowadays, millions of people feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 725351.0,
      "end_time": 727857.0,
      "text": "that their jobs have little meaning or significance."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 727881.0,
      "end_time": 730698.0,
      "text": "A recent poll among 230,000 employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 730722.0,
      "end_time": 732627.0,
      "text": "in 142 countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 732652.0,
      "end_time": 737317.0,
      "text": "found that only 13 percent of workers actually like their job."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 738420.0,
      "end_time": 742870.0,
      "text": "And another poll found that as much as 37 percent of British workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 742111.0,
      "end_time": 745400.0,
      "text": "have a job that they think doesn&#39;t even need to exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 746207.0,
      "end_time": 748501.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like Brad Pitt says in \"Fight Club,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 748525.0,
      "end_time": 752180.0,
      "text": "\"Too often we&#39;re working jobs we hate so we can buy shit we don&#39;t need.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 752205.0,
      "end_time": 753683.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 753707.0,
      "end_time": 755104.0,
      "text": "Now, don&#39;t get me wrong --"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 755128.0,
      "end_time": 757682.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not talking about the teachers and the garbagemen"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 757706.0,
      "end_time": 759188.0,
      "text": "and the care workers here."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 759212.0,
      "end_time": 760826.0,
      "text": "If they stopped working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 760850.0,
      "end_time": 762167.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d be in trouble."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 762810.0,
      "end_time": 766435.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m talking about all those well-paid professionals with excellent résumés"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 766459.0,
      "end_time": 768263.0,
      "text": "who earn their money doing ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 768288.0,
      "end_time": 770324.0,
      "text": "strategic transactor peer-to-peer meetings"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 770348.0,
      "end_time": 773380.0,
      "text": "while brainstorming the value add-on of disruptive co-creation"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 773404.0,
      "end_time": 774577.0,
      "text": "in the network society."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 774601.0,
      "end_time": 775624.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 775648.0,
      "end_time": 776666.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 776690.0,
      "end_time": 777892.0,
      "text": "Or something like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 777916.0,
      "end_time": 780840.0,
      "text": "Just imagine again how much talent we&#39;re wasting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 780864.0,
      "end_time": 784704.0,
      "text": "simply because we tell our kids they&#39;ll have to \"earn a living.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 785458.0,
      "end_time": 789199.0,
      "text": "Or think of what a math whiz working at Facebook lamented a few years ago:"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 789224.0,
      "end_time": 791860.0,
      "text": "\"The best minds of my generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 791110.0,
      "end_time": 794223.0,
      "text": "are thinking about how to make people click ads.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 796519.0,
      "end_time": 797764.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a historian."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 798812.0,
      "end_time": 800881.0,
      "text": "And if history teaches us anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 800905.0,
      "end_time": 803697.0,
      "text": "it is that things could be different."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 803721.0,
      "end_time": 805112.0,
      "text": "There is nothing inevitable"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 805136.0,
      "end_time": 808930.0,
      "text": "about the way we structured our society and economy right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 808117.0,
      "end_time": 810473.0,
      "text": "Ideas can and do change the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 810497.0,
      "end_time": 813700.0,
      "text": "And I think that especially in the past few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 813320.0,
      "end_time": 814461.0,
      "text": "it has become abundantly clear"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 814485.0,
      "end_time": 816438.0,
      "text": "that we cannot stick to the status quo --"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 816462.0,
      "end_time": 818370.0,
      "text": "that we need new ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 820319.0,
      "end_time": 823531.0,
      "text": "I know that many of you may feel pessimistic"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 823556.0,
      "end_time": 825619.0,
      "text": "about a future of rising inequality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 825643.0,
      "end_time": 826920.0,
      "text": "xenophobia"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 826944.0,
      "end_time": 828140.0,
      "text": "and climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 828806.0,
      "end_time": 831240.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not enough to know what we&#39;re against."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 831480.0,
      "end_time": 832660.0,
      "text": "We also need to be for something."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 832684.0,
      "end_time": 835218.0,
      "text": "Martin Luther King didn&#39;t say, \"I have a nightmare.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 835242.0,
      "end_time": 837115.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 837139.0,
      "end_time": 838298.0,
      "text": "He had a dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 838322.0,
      "end_time": 839401.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 839425.0,
      "end_time": 840577.0,
      "text": "So ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 841655.0,
      "end_time": 842880.0,
      "text": "here&#39;s my dream:"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 844123.0,
      "end_time": 845761.0,
      "text": "I believe in a future"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 845785.0,
      "end_time": 848137.0,
      "text": "where the value of your work is not determined"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 848162.0,
      "end_time": 849639.0,
      "text": "by the size of your paycheck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 849663.0,
      "end_time": 851695.0,
      "text": "but by the amount of happiness you spread"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 851719.0,
      "end_time": 853696.0,
      "text": "and the amount of meaning you give."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 853720.0,
      "end_time": 854952.0,
      "text": "I believe in a future"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 854976.0,
      "end_time": 858636.0,
      "text": "where the point of education is not to prepare you for another useless job"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 858660.0,
      "end_time": 860270.0,
      "text": "but for a life well-lived."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 861240.0,
      "end_time": 862303.0,
      "text": "I believe in a future"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 862327.0,
      "end_time": 865421.0,
      "text": "where an existence without poverty is not a privilege"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 865445.0,
      "end_time": 867458.0,
      "text": "but a right we all deserve."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 867482.0,
      "end_time": 868947.0,
      "text": "So here we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 868971.0,
      "end_time": 870122.0,
      "text": "Here we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 870146.0,
      "end_time": 872336.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got the research, we&#39;ve got the evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 872360.0,
      "end_time": 873523.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ve got the means."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 873547.0,
      "end_time": 877456.0,
      "text": "Now, more than 500 years after Thomas More first wrote about a basic income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 877480.0,
      "end_time": 881535.0,
      "text": "and 100 years after George Orwell discovered the true nature of poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 881559.0,
      "end_time": 884000.0,
      "text": "we all need to change our worldview,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 884240.0,
      "end_time": 887130.0,
      "text": "because poverty is not a lack of character."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 887652.0,
      "end_time": 890220.0,
      "text": "Poverty is a lack of cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 891141.0,
      "end_time": 892324.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 892349.0,
      "end_time": 896772.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}